\frac{\frac{c}{b} - 1}{\frac{c}{b} - 1} &= 1 \\
1 &= \frac{c}{b} - 1 \\
\frac{b}{c} &= b
\end{align*} \begin{align*}
\frac{c}{b} - 1 &= \frac{4}{c} - 1\\
\frac{c}{b} &= \frac{4}{c}\\
b &= \frac{c^2}{4}.
\end{align*}

## Step 6: Substitute a^2 = b into b = \frac{c^2}{4}
\begin{align*}
a^2 &= \frac{c^2}{4} \\
4a^2 &= c^2
\end{align*}

